show.title: I am the Woman of the Jianghu
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/5cp98UrkLcUtRSQv5
show.description: Nithya, a young woman, meets with a mysterious accident under surveillance ,only to awaken to a truth that shatters her reality: she is the reincarnation of Suriya, a revolutionary prince.As past and present collide, Nithya uncovers her ties to the powerful Shiohan Group, where Suriya its rightful heir once stood at the heart of a deadly web of love, betrayal, and political conspiracy.Now, she must navigate a world of enemies and hidden agendas, where reclaiming her past could change the fate of the future.
